statements: SELECT * FROM business_performance_dashboard;
SELECT dashboard_name, kpi_1 FROM business_performance_dashboard ORDER BY kpi_1 DESC;
SELECT dashboard_name, kpi_2 FROM business_performance_dashboard WHERE kpi_2 > 50;
SELECT dashboard_id, dashboard_name, kpi_1 + kpi_2 + kpi_3 AS total_kpi FROM business_performance_dashboard;
SELECT * FROM business_performance_dashboard WHERE kpi_1 > kpi_2 AND kpi_2 < 100;
SELECT * FROM business_performance_dashboard ORDER BY dashboard_name DESC, kpi_1 ASC, kpi_2 DESC;
SELECT dashboard_id, dashboard_name, kpi_1 + kpi_2 AS total_kpi, kpi_3 FROM business_performance_dashboard WHERE kpi_1 > 100 AND kpi_3 < 50;
SELECT * FROM business_performance_dashboard WHERE kpi_1 BETWEEN 50 AND 100;
SELECT AVG(kpi_1) AS avg_kpi_1, SUM(kpi_2) AS total_kpi_2 FROM business_performance_dashboard;
SELECT dashboard_name, kpi_1, kpi_2, kpi_3 FROM business_performance_dashboard WHERE kpi_1 > kpi_2 AND kpi_2 > 0 LIMIT 5;
SELECT name, value FROM key_performance_indicators;
SELECT * FROM business_data WHERE revenue > 1000;
SELECT timestamp, revenue, cost FROM business_data ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT id, name, value FROM key_performance_indicators WHERE value < 50;
SELECT entry_id, timestamp, profit FROM business_data WHERE profit = (revenue - cost);
SELECT * FROM key_performance_indicators WHERE value > 100 ORDER BY name DESC;
SELECT name, value FROM key_performance_indicators WHERE id IN (1, 3, 5);
SELECT MAX(revenue), MIN(cost), AVG(profit) FROM business_data WHERE timestamp >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT id, name, value FROM key_performance_indicators WHERE name LIKE '%profit%';
SELECT * FROM business_data WHERE revenue > cost ORDER BY timestamp ASC LIMIT 10;
SELECT * FROM dashboard_metrics;
SELECT kpi_name, kpi_value FROM dashboard_metrics WHERE kpi_value > 100;
SELECT * FROM business_data ORDER BY revenue DESC;
SELECT username, email FROM dashboard_users WHERE role = 'admin';
SELECT business_name, revenue, expenses, profit FROM business_data WHERE profit < 0;
SELECT * FROM dashboard_metrics WHERE kpi_value > 100 ORDER BY created_at DESC;
SELECT kpi_name, kpi_value FROM dashboard_metrics WHERE created_at > '2022-01-01' AND kpi_value BETWEEN 50 AND 200;
SELECT business_name, profit FROM business_data WHERE revenue > expenses ORDER BY profit DESC;
SELECT user_id, username, role FROM dashboard_users WHERE role = 'Admin';
SELECT * FROM dashboard_metrics dm JOIN dashboard_users du ON dm.id = du.user_id WHERE dm.kpi_value < 100 AND du.role = 'Manager';
SELECT * FROM KPI_Dashboard ORDER BY KPI_Name DESC;
SELECT KPI_Name, KPI_Target FROM KPI_Dashboard WHERE KPI_Current_Value > 1000;
SELECT KPI_Description FROM KPI_Dashboard WHERE KPI_ID = 3;
SELECT * FROM Business_Data ORDER BY Industry_Type, Revenue DESC;
SELECT Business_Name, Revenue FROM Business_Data WHERE Employee_Count > 5000;

SELECT KPI_Name, KPI_Target FROM KPI_Dashboard
SELECT Business_Name, Industry_Type, Revenue FROM Business_Data ORDER BY Revenue DESC

SELECT User_Name, User_Role FROM Dashboard_Users WHERE User_Role = 'Viewer' ORDER BY User_Name
SELECT metric_name, metric_value FROM dashboard_metrics;
SELECT sale_amount, sale_date FROM sales_data;
SELECT product_name, product_price FROM products WHERE product_category = 'Electronics';
SELECT customer_name, customer_email, customer_city FROM customers ORDER BY customer_name DESC;
SELECT order_date, product_id, customer_id FROM orders WHERE order_id > 100 ORDER BY order_date ASC;
SELECT metric_name, metric_value FROM dashboard_metrics WHERE metric_value > 100 ORDER BY metric_name ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT sale_amount, sale_date, product_name FROM sales_data INNER JOIN products ON sales_data.product_id = products.product_id WHERE product_category = 'Electronics' ORDER BY sale_date DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT customer_name, customer_city FROM customers WHERE customer_city LIKE 'New%' AND LENGTH(customer_name) > 10 ORDER BY customer_name ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT product_name, product_price FROM products WHERE product_price BETWEEN 50 AND 100 ORDER BY product_price DESC LIMIT 5;

SELECT order_id, order_date, customer_name, product_name FROM orders INNER JOIN customers ON orders.customer_id = customers.customer_id INNER JOIN products ON orders.product_id = products.product_id ORDER BY order_date DESC LIMIT 5;
